title: REDEEM FAILED

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body:
I got honor capsule and in it I got 3 key frags and premanent skin of grey warwick.
When i tried to unlock the skin it says REDEEM FAILED.

PLS help

replies.body: This was a recent issue that seems like it's recurring this morning.  If this is still happening for you, can you try spamming redeem to see if it budges through?  You may need to first restart your client as well.
